User Settings forms now have better javascript validation.
UsingFormValidation Jquery plugin (check http://http://formvalidation.io/)
Add placeholder to inputs and edit userDuplicate method

Finish validation for every user form
+ Added javascript validation (Bootstrap Validation) to every user form see http://formvalidation.io/) + Removed Ajax Request from SignupForm (useless) + Added single methods for username duplicate and email duplicate

Update UserAccount forms
+ Added js validator to SecurityQuestionForm + Fixed js validator after seding Ajax Request + Changed resetPassword link from ?token=token to /token

Work at User templates and projects
+ created Addsite form ++note: if subdomain exists concatenate subdomain and lastSiteId + 1 + created user projects, which show all user's projects and gives posbility to Preview project and edit it + after signIn, user is redirected to his projects + in userOptions is added Projects item which leads to User's Projects
